snippet.title: Kronorite CTF Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/876780/Kronorite/

Kronorite is a nice little casual arcade game that you can hop into when you're bored and play with up to 10 people (5 vs 5). This trailer showcases gameplay from the CTF game mode which recently received a big improvement regarding bots.


Discord: https://discord.kronorite.com
Website: https://kronorite.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Kronorite
Email: hello@kronorite.com
